name: "➕ Add a film stock or lab"
description: Request a new film stock or lab be added to the presets
title: "[Add] "
labels: ["data", "enhancement"]
body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        Presets aim to cover **mainstream, readily available** stocks and labs. Rare, limited-run,
        novelty, or frequently-out-of-stock films are generally left out on purpose — you can always
        add them yourself in the Library tab without them shipping as a preset.

  - type: dropdown
    id: kind
    attributes:
      label: What should be added?
      options:
        - A film stock
        - A lab
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: input
    id: name
    attributes:
      label: Name
      placeholder: "e.g. Kodak Portra 400 (120), or Hillvale Photo Melbourne"
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: film-details
    attributes:
      label: Film details (skip if requesting a lab)
      value: |
        - Format (35mm / 120 / 110 / …): 
        - Box speed (ISO): 
        - Process (C41 / BW / E6 / ECN-2): 
        - Exposures per roll: 
        - Push/pull limit in stops (maxPushPull): 
        - Regular price (not sale price): 
        - Where to buy (link): 
    validations:
      required: false

  - type: textarea
    id: lab-details
    attributes:
      label: Lab details (skip if requesting a film)
      description: One block per service tier — copy the block if the lab offers several.
      value: |
        - Address: 
        - Website: 
        - Service tier: 
          - Development cost per roll: 
          - Push/pull fee (and whether it's per-stop or flat): 
          - Turnaround (next day / same week / longer): 
          - Hi-res scan? (yes/no): 
          - Processes handled (C41 / BW / E6 / ECN-2): 
    validations:
      required: false

  - type: input
    id: source
    attributes:
      label: Source link
      description: The retailer or lab page with current pricing.
      placeholder: "https://…"
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: screenshot
    attributes:
      label: Screenshot (optional but helpful)
      description: |
        A screenshot of the pricing page preserves what you saw, since prices and stock change.
        Drag an image into this box to upload it.
      placeholder: Paste or drag your screenshot here.
    validations:
      required: false

  - type: checkboxes
    id: confirm
    attributes:
      label: Confirmations
      options:
        - label: This is a mainstream stock/lab that's reliably available (not a rare or limited run)
        - label: The price given is the **regular** price, not a sale price
